      "\\(\\dfrac{\\pi}{2}\\)",
      "\\(\\dfrac{\\pi}{4}\\)",
      "\\(0\\)"
    ],
    "correctIndex": 2,
    "explanation": "Let \\(I=\\int_0^{\\pi/2}\\dfrac{\\cos^{2020}x}{\\cos^{2020}x+\\sin^{2020}x}dx\\) …(i)\n\nUsing \\(a\\to\\pi/2-x\\): \\(I=\\int_0^{\\pi/2}\\dfrac{\\sin^{2020}x}{\\sin^{2020}x+\\cos^{2020}x}dx\\) …(ii)\n\n\\(2I=\\int_0^{\\pi/2}dx=\\dfrac{\\pi}{2}\\implies I=\\dfrac{\\pi}{4}\\)",
    "name": "King Property with High Power Trig"
  },
  {
