      "\\(6\\)",
      "\\(8\\)",
      "\\(2\\)"
    ],
    "correctIndex": 1,
    "explanation": "Since the integrand is even:\n\n\\(I=2\\int_0^{\\pi/2}(2\\sin x+\\cos x)dx=2[-2\\cos x+\\sin x]_0^{\\pi/2}=2[(0+1)-(-2+0)]=2(3)=6\\)",
    "name": "Even Function Integration"
  },
  {
    "id": "m27_item17",
    "text": "\\(\\displaystyle\\int_0^1(1+x)\\log(1+x)\\,dx=\\)",
    "options": [
      "\\(-\\dfrac{3}{4}+\\log2\\)",
      "\\(\\dfrac{3}{4}+2\\log2\\)",
