      "\\(\\dfrac{35}{72}\\)"
    ],
    "correctIndex": 2,
    "explanation": "Rewriting as Riemann sum: \\(\\displaystyle\\lim_{n\\to\\infty}\\sum_{r=0}^{4n}\\dfrac{n^2}{(n+r)^3}=\\int_0^4\\dfrac{dx}{(1+x)^3}=\\left[-\\dfrac{1}{2(1+x)^2}\\right]_0^4=\\dfrac{1}{2}-\\dfrac{1}{50}=\\dfrac{12}{25}\\)",
    "name": "Limit as Riemann Sum"
  },
  {
